@startuml sequence_prediction
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Predictive Maintenance Pipeline

participant "Timer Trigger\n(2 AM UTC)" as Timer
participant "PredictiveMaintenance\nFunction" as PMF
database "SQL Server 2022" as DB
participant "Azure OpenAI\nService" as AI
participant "NotificationPipeline" as Notif
participant "SignalR Hub" as SR

Timer -> PMF: Daily trigger (2 AM UTC)

PMF -> DB: Query equipment with\n>=30 days telemetry data
DB --> PMF: Equipment list

loop For each equipment
    PMF -> DB: SELECT telemetry events\n(last 30+ days)\naggregated by metric
    DB --> PMF: Telemetry aggregates\n(engine hours, temp, fuel)

    PMF -> DB: SELECT service history\n(work orders, parts replaced)
    DB --> PMF: Historical service records

    PMF -> AI: Analyze failure patterns\n{telemetry, service history,\nequipment model}
    AI --> PMF: Predictions per component\n{component, probability,\ntimeframe, action}

    PMF -> DB: UPSERT AIPrediction records\n(confidence, priority,\nrecommended action)
end

PMF -> DB: SELECT new high-priority\npredictions (confidence >= 0.8)
DB --> PMF: High-priority predictions

alt High-priority predictions exist
    PMF -> Notif: TriggerHighPriorityAlert\n(predictions list)
    Notif -> SR: Push to Fleet Managers\n(real-time notification)
    Notif -> Notif: Queue email via\nLogic Apps
end

PMF -> PMF: Log run summary\nvia Serilog to\nApp Insights

@enduml
